ethan.bio: Ethan James Caldwell is a graduate of George Washington University (GW). Born and raised in Washington, Ethan has had a lifelong passion for cars, motorcycles, and all things automotive. From a young age, he was captivated by the mechanics, design, and culture surrounding vehicles, which eventually inspired his career. Ethan currently drives a silver 2005 Honda Accord, a testament to his appreciation for reliable and timeless vehicles.
